import * as React from 'react'
import {
    List, 
    Datagrid, 
    TextField, 
    EmailField, 
    UrlField,
    Create,
    SimpleForm,
    ReferenceInput, TextInput,
} from 'react-admin'

export const TypeList = props => (
    <List {...props}>
        <Datagrid>
            <TextField source="type" />
        </Datagrid>
    </List>
);
